<subSubSection id="7B762DAB0C2171761822B1BAE0D19CC4" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" type="notes">
<paragraph id="37315BD9D14223C6D47B880490C727B7" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CA5D2B25F03EE435B75E64E6452878BE" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">
First record for Bulgaria. 
<emphasis id="328F134B82E653EFB7589CE2EEE32D3C" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Western Pre-Balkan</emphasis>
: Belgradchishki Skali, 03.v.2015, 1♂; 
<emphasis id="4D0FE3F144614704724AA54BCBC78B94" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Western Stara Planina</emphasis>
: Slivnitsa vill., Aldomirovsko Blato, 18.iii.2017, 3♂♂ and 10♀♀; same location, 10.vii.2011, 1♂; 
<emphasis id="A3DC034C63D692676DE2CA6CFB9071A3" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Middle Stara Planina</emphasis>
: Divchovoto vill., 08.v.2015, 1♂ and 1♀. Detailed occurrence data: 
<bibRefCitation id="1EC2FC2E31AE9116524E47A81D3F41C9" author="Gjonov, I." journalOrPublisher="Annals of the Upper Silesian Museum in Bytom. Entomology" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" refId="B7727581" refString="Gjonov, I., 2022. new_fulgoromorpha_records_bulgaria_2022. In: Biodiversity Data Journal. Occurrence dataset." title="new _ fulgoromorpha _ records _ bulgaria _ 2022" volumeTitle="Biodiversity Data Journal. Occurrence dataset." year="2022">Gjonov (2022)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D32478B101964DD60B8D3FEB699ED237" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">
<emphasis id="0A927AF2DAF3AD5F2EE8CCFBB3217456" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Red Lists</emphasis>
: It is assessed as not endangered in some countries of Central Europe.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DD47A1847869EAEC5B82DC72CE854469" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">
<emphasis id="6B2489A3A69F37728E00D9872AE413DF" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Host plant</emphasis>
: 
<taxonomicName id="83E6EF4C2E677E10830DA40F65C34FCF" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Phalaris" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Phalaris arundinacea" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="arundinacea">
<emphasis id="D2CCED39497C520088BC32DECB1E6AD5" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Phalaris arundinacea</emphasis>
